				<wikidot:authorName>coachskau</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>399974</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>From what I understand, their perception of plants being mechanical objects starts to alter their reality, meaning they eventually need welding tools to cut open the SCP (presumably other plants, as well) and culminating in eating plants being like actually eating pieces of metal.</p> 
				 	]]>
